{
  "stem": "24195.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'd like to come back to that comment that I made earlier about when the clinic was totally bombed out and the building was destroyed and were maybe about 30 or 40 casualties among the patients.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And but I think this governess-- her name was Marie-- she was the only casualty from the staff that was-- she was in the elevator.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, I was trying to-- you know, I tried to stand guard at the beginning at the entrance to the clinic and put on that air warden's helmet.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after a while, my mother came over and says, take it off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Put your regular cap on and hat on because you look like a member of the Jewish brigade.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think what she meant was that she-- I'm in the wrong place at the wrong time looking like I am, and that I might provoke somebody and get somebody thinking that, you know, what's this?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He looks so Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was even more expressed my, my Jewish looks by enhancing my Jewish looks by having that helmet on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so that's-- that was not a good thing to do at this time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Could you explain what you mean by Jewish looks?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my, my, my looks, I mean, my face.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because people were identified by their looks a lot a times being as Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Could be eyes, hair, could be nose, could be anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there's a certain look about some-- and it's not always true, I mean.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of people of other races, of other backgrounds, a lot of Italians, sometimes Greeks, could also be--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Arabs too, identified as Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at that particular time, that's what she meant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She did not want, want me to cause any attention, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
